{"text_id":214501,"tokens":["This"," article"," examines"," the"," features"," of"," sem","im","art","ingale"," reflecting"," Brownian","motions"," (","SR","B","Ms",")"," that"," exist"," within"," the"," boundaries"," of"," domains"," with"," piece","w","ises","m","ooth"," edges","."," An"," invariance"," principle"," is"," presented"," which"," can"," be"," applied"," to","ensure"," adequate"," conditions"," for"," SR","B","Ms",","," with"," the"," exception"," of"," small"," random","variations"," in"," the"," defining"," parameters","."," This"," perturbation"," result"," is"," used"," to","assess"," the"," existence"," of"," SR","B","Ms"," under"," certain"," conditions",","," as"," well"," as"," for","valid","ating"," approximations"," with"," either"," SR","B","Ms"," in"," convex"," poly","hed","rons"," or"," in"," bounded","domains"," with"," piecewise"," smooth"," boundaries","."," An"," important"," factor"," in"," the"," proof"," ofthe"," invariance"," principle"," is"," a"," type"," of"," oscillation"," inequality"," associated"," with","the"," perturbed"," Skor","ok","hod"," problem","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"davinci","label":1}